retion rates and resolve the tension between theoretical\nmodels and observational constraints on the properties of cold CGM gas.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Aug 2020 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Sep 2020 04:08:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-11"}
