 magnetic), and argue that analogous generalisations of the\ninversion symmetries exist both for the static and the rotating cases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Aug 2020 18:12:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-14"}
