irical study to evaluate the effectiveness and\nusability of the proposed testing framework. Results show that the overall\nreplay accuracy reaches around 63.39% on Android (14% improvement over\nstate-of-the-art approaches) and 21.83% on iOS (98% improvement over\nstate-of-the-art approaches).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Aug 2020 08:59:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Feb 2021 05:26:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 22 Feb 2021 01:39:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-23"}
