ing mindfulness practice with a robot. We believe that our findings driven\nfrom an ecologically valid setting, can be used in development of future BCI\nsystems that are integrated with social robots for health applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Aug 2020 13:29:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-13"}
